{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_28ada805effeKVkAJHcvBKMXXi","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d7525ab240010H5F1WSUaqtVjl","parts":[{"id":"prt_d7525b33d002uVsCyoW1bV0VfK","messageID":"msg_d7525ab240010H5F1WSUaqtVjl","sessionID":"ses_28ada805effeKVkAJHcvBKMXXi","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_a82438c1e8784a0c812717c1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/workspace/AGENTS.md"},"output":"<path>/workspace/AGENTS.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>1: # Agent Instructions\n2: \n3: ## Tox\n4: \n5: - Always run tox from the main `tox.venv`\n6: - If there is no `tox.venv`, create one with `python -m venv tox.venv`, activate it and run `pip install tox`\n7: \n8: ## Package Manager\n9: \n10: Use **tox** for testing (not pytest directly):\n11: - Test matrix configuration is in `tox.ini`\n12: - Integration tests: `tox -e py3.14-{integration}-v{version}`\n13: - Common tests: `tox -e py3.14-common`\n14: - Run specific test file: `TESTPATH=tests/integrations/logging/test_logging.py tox -e py3.14-common`\n15: - Run single test: `TESTPATH=tests/path/to/test_file.py tox -e py3.14-common -- -k \"test_name\"`\n16: \n17: ## Type Checking\n18: \n19: Use **tox** for type checking (not mypy directly):\n20: - Run `tox -e mypy` before committing (must pass with zero errors)\n21: - Strict mode enabled (`check_untyped_defs`, `disallow_untyped_defs`)\n22: \n23: ## Linting & Formatting\n24: \n25: Use **tox** for linting (not ruff directly):\n26: - `tox -e ruff`\n27: - Full lint suite: `tox -e linters`\n28: - Full lint suite must pass before committing\n29: \n30: ## Commit Attribution\n31: \n32: AI commits MUST include:\n33: ```\n34: Co-Authored-By: <agent model name> <noreply@anthropic.com>\n35: ```\n36: Example: `Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>`\n37: \n38: ## Auto-Generated Files\n39: \n40: Do NOT edit these directly — modify source scripts instead:\n41: - `tox.ini` — generated by `scripts/populate_tox/populate_tox.py` from `scripts/populate_tox/tox.jinja`\n42: - `.github/workflows/test-integrations-*.yml` — generated by `scripts/split_tox_gh_actions/split_tox_gh_actions.py`\n43: - Regenerate all: `scripts/generate-test-files.sh`\n44: \n45: ## Adding Integrations to Test Suite\n46: \n47: 1. Add minimum version to `_MIN_VERSIONS` in `sentry_sdk/integrations/__init__.py`\n48: 2. Add config to `TEST_SUITE_CONFIG` in `scripts/populate_tox/config.py`\n49: 3. Add to group in `scripts/split_tox_gh_actions/split_tox_gh_actions.py`\n50: 4. Run `scripts/generate-test-files.sh`\n51: \n52: ## Integration Contract\n53: \n54: - Don't crash applications or swallow exceptions\n55: - Don't mutate object references or alter function signatures\n56: - Don't leak file descriptors or make unexpected DB requests\n57: - Write defensive code\n58: - Use end-to-end tests (not mocks)\n59: \n60: ## Key Paths\n61: \n62: | Path | Description |\n63: |------|-------------|\n64: | `sentry_sdk/integrations/` | integration modules |\n65: | `sentry_sdk/ai/` | AI monitoring |\n66: | `sentry_sdk/crons/` | Cron monitoring |\n67: | `sentry_sdk/profiler/` | Performance profiling |\n68: | `tests/integrations/{name}/` | Integration test suites |\n69: | `scripts/populate_tox/config.py` | Test suite configuration |\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Agent Instructions\n\n## Tox\n\n- Always run tox from the main `tox.venv`\n- If there is no `tox.venv`, create one with `python -m venv tox.venv`, activate it and run `pip install tox`\n\n## Package Manager\n\nUse **tox** for testing (not pytest directly):\n- Test matrix configuration is in `tox.ini`\n- Integration tests: `tox -e py3.14-{integration}-v{version}`\n- Common tests: `tox -e py3.14-common`\n- Run specific test file: `TESTPATH=tests/integrations/logging/test_logging.py tox -e py3.14-common`\n- Run single test: `TESTPATH=tests/path/to/test_file.py tox -e py3.14-common -- -k \"test_name\"`\n\n## Type Checking\n\nUse **tox** for type checking (not mypy directly):\n- Run `tox -e mypy` before committing (must pass with zero errors)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"AGENTS.md","time":{"start":1775786898669,"end":1775786898671}}}]}
